--------------------------------------------------------------------

 Path to guestbook.cgi

 guestbook.cgi needs to be in your cgi-bin directory.  You will
 probably want to consult with your isp on how to set up
 cgi scripts.

--------------------------------------------------------------------

 Modify guestbook.cgi as per the instructions in guestbook.cgi.  Please
 note that it is assumed that one has some knowledge of Perl.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

 See signguest.html and guestbook.html in the examples directory
 for hints on setting up a guestbook.

    guestbook.html - display guestbook entries
    signguest.html - form for adding an entry in a guestbook

